INSERT INTO `beritas` VALUES (1, 1, 1, '{\"en\":\"Orthopedic and other rehabilitation centers\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Orthopedic medicine deals with muscles and bones. Physical therapists are typically the practitioner patients see for problems in these areas of the body. If you are experiencing chronic lower back pain, for example, you might see a physical therapist at an orthopedic center or clinic to get a diagnosis and a plan of treatment.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Orthopedic centers deal in everything from athletic injuries to therapy for patients with disabilities. They typically offer evaluation and diagnosis of the problem, as well as prevention, treatment and rehabilitation work involving bone, tendon, ligament, muscle and joint conditions.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">These healthcare facilities have a variety of names depending on their specialization. They might simple be called outpatient physical therapy centers. Or you could find pediatric physical therapy clinics, sports medicine centers or geriatric physical therapy clinics.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">There are also rehabilitation centers where patients can receive&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.naric.com\\/?q=en\\/content\\/what-rehabilitation-center\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">various therapies<\\/a>&nbsp;to help restore their abilities after an illness or injury. Physical therapy, occupational therapy and speech therapy are all processes that help people gain or regain skills they need to move around, work or speak in daily life.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Practitioners at rehabilitation centers work with people to help them recover as much of their mobility and independence as possible. Outpatient rehab centers can relieve the strain on hospital rehabilitation floors.<\\/p>\"}', 'berita/x8YDQNjBq18CnbhsXuB40yL4PffcaDtQiQlxbT2w.png', '[]', NULL, '2021-01-09 13:01:50', '2021-01-09 13:30:38', 'slug-1');
INSERT INTO `beritas` VALUES (2, 1, 1, '{\"en\":\"Mental health and addiction treatment centers\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">This type of healthcare facility is a grouping for many different types of facilities. Specialty treatment centers exist all across America for specified mental health issues and addictions.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Mental health treatment facilities sometimes exist as a general institution for any mental health issue and are sometimes specialized. Examples of these kinds of facilities are suicidal thoughts (or suicidal ideation) treatment, depression treatment, trauma and post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) treatment, treatment for anxiety disorders, behavioral disorders and more.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">You can find inpatient or outpatient versions of many mental health facilities, designed to assist patients through different stages of their healing processes. At the acute-care level, you can find mental health wards in hospitals\\u2014as well as&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.mentalhealthamerica.net\\/hospitalization\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">hospitals specifically devoted to mental health<\\/a>&nbsp;and long-term care facilities.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Addiction treatment centers typically deal with&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/americanaddictioncenters.org\\/adult-addiction-treatment-programs\\/\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">drug and alcohol addictions<\\/a>, as well as problematic behavioral addictions like gambling, work, shopping or the internet.<\\/p>\"}', 'berita/bpWLCSQpY5QPdb177ANHVs111Kr9uMTzZEew1swi.jpg', '[\"gallery-berita\\/uI48Ol9CbPy8DslC3lKlg2uKYAqOgyxPz1M2LBgz.jpg\",\"gallery-berita\\/6JYOMKu0RVvZocL3Ct7YqXZNf8j9AiTVsrjGgLFr.jpg\",\"gallery-berita\\/SbsXYfxoP8mvo3S7ZWOhBjkBSJkOFkNhwFFPFfN2.jpg\",\"gallery-berita\\/lSKvBUI3eFvxAhCgRT6rEIBYwxvqF549eviB7QNS.jpg\"]', NULL, '2021-01-09 13:02:54', '2021-01-10 11:08:03', 'slug-2');
INSERT INTO `beritas` VALUES (3, 1, 1, '{\"en\":\"Nursing homes\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Nursing homes offer a living situation for patients whose medical needs aren\\u2019t severe enough for hospitalization, but are too serious to manage at home. Some nursing homes offer services for heavier medical needs, such as speech and occupational therapy. Other nursing homes try to create a homier atmosphere, and might operate like an apartment complex with medical staff on hand.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">According to the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.longtermcarelink.net\\/eldercare\\/nursing_home.htm\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">National Care Planning Council&nbsp;<\\/a>(NCPC), nursing homes enable patients with injuries, acute illnesses or postoperative care needs to recover in an environment outside the hospital. These facilities offer long-term medical care ranging from simple to complex levels of need in an environment built for residents to live in long term instead of just staying a few weeks or months.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Many people picture elderly patients in a nursing home. For the most part that\\u2019s true\\u2014<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.longtermcarelink.net\\/eldercare\\/nursing_home.htm\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">over 80<\\/a>&nbsp;percent of patients are over the age of 65. But there are also younger patients in nursing homes who may have serious long-term illnesses and need care beyond what their families can provide.<\\/p>\"}', 'berita/eYbVVi2hi3ZSBu1RitySV5VSbj2P7M0ORUXBg7mX.jpg', '[]', NULL, '2021-01-09 13:03:53', '2021-01-09 13:03:53', 'slug-3');
