e=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">various therapies<\\/a>&nbsp;to help restore their abilities after an illness or injury. Physical therapy, occupational therapy and speech therapy are all processes that help people gain or regain skills they need to move around, work or speak in daily life.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Practitioners at rehabilitation centers work with people to help them recover as much of their mobility and independence as possible. Outpatient rehab centers can relieve the strain on hospital rehabilitation floors.<\\/p>\"}', 'berita/eYbVVi2hi3ZSBu1RitySV5VSbj2P7M0ORUXBg7mX.jpg', '[\"gallery-berita\\/p5Ca1n80ENEMzqNXXBuQe5welbUbCdkzSMCm60dI.png\",\"gallery-berita\\/30MFqUK2hNIllUiqsNsW6o4Qwr4vlTC0SzlOOjll.jpg\",\"gallery-berita\\/7oxNYhXx2lxF5HHdwbtprkmJHQHpph9B8vCVqqSO.jpg\",\"gallery-berita\\/2KhDq4XkLQkzmSc1zjoHM9W3IsdXnMHnhLoONeYl.jpg\"]', NULL, '2021-01-09 13:36:42', '2021-01-09 13:36:42', 'slug-4');

