INSERT INTO `fasilitas` VALUES (1, 1, '{\"en\":\"Ambulatory surgical centers\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Ambulatory surgical centers, also called outpatient surgical facilities, allow patients to receive certain surgical procedures outside a hospital environment. These environments often offer surgeries at a<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.ascassociation.org\\/advancingsurgicalcare\\/aboutascs\\/industryoverview\\/apositivetrendinhealthcare\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">&nbsp;lower cost than hospitals<\\/a>&nbsp;while also reducing the risk of exposure to infection\\u2014since patients are there for surgery, not to recover from sickness and disease.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Ambulatory surgical centers don\\u2019t provide diagnostic services or clinic hours. Instead, they take patients who have been referred for surgery by a hospital or physician\\u2014they\\u2019re designed to be \\u201call business\\u201d when it comes to surgical care.<\\/p>\"}', 'fasilitas/pRS5pI0eADZvbNMWJCQ4Qzt0BObglz5VW627GDAC.jpg', '[\"gallerys\\/6aInH6RYK2gCmvpwpkEsujhM4JWVHXstNTWOBEjg.jpg\",\"gallerys\\/S21Qv8Ul2bavAeaMvtcQh0LLfiS7iSe4rghEO7WO.jpg\",\"gallerys\\/X25g2gda8zygocvB8cbZwHm3yU8rur0FgDadAclb.jpg\",\"gallerys\\/FmNNy9aamcJFArIhso4QaI9hMFGBDxh1TXPRJq1N.jpg\"]', NULL, '2021-01-09 05:05:49', '2021-01-09 05:34:19', 'abulance-center');
INSERT INTO `fasilitas` VALUES (3, 1, '{\"en\":\"Birth centers\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">A birth center is a healthcare facility for childbirth that focuses on the midwifery model, according to the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.birthcenters.org\\/?page=bce_what_is_a_bc\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">American Association of Birth Centers<\\/a>. They aim to create a birth environment that feels more comfortable to the mother and allows for a cost-effective, family-inclusive birth.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Birth centers are not typically equipped with the same contingency equipment and staff as a hospital, such as surgeons in case of a C-section or a neonatal intensive care unit. As a result, birth centers accommodate only healthy pregnancies without any known risk or complication factors.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">These facilities are guided by principles of prevention, sensitivity, safety, cost-effectiveness and appropriate medical intervention when needed.<\\/p>\"}', 'fasilitas/jaM1Kgg2WMbEOxZmv4Ty5TqhOPcQpvLztcuPqpMt.jpg', '[]', NULL, '2021-01-09 05:13:42', '2021-01-09 05:13:42', 'birth-centers');
INSERT INTO `fasilitas` VALUES (4, 1, '{\"en\":\"Blood banks\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Blood banks allow donors to donate blood and platelets while also storing and sorting blood into components that can be used most effectively by patients.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">\\u201cRed blood cells carry oxygen, platelets help the blood clot and plasma has specific proteins that allows proper regulation of coagulation and healing,\\u201d writes the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.hematology.org\\/Patients\\/Basics\\/Banking.aspx\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">American Society of Hematology<\\/a>. Sometimes patients need these particular components specifically, and sometimes they just need lots of blood. For example, a single car accident victim&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.redcrossblood.org\\/learn-about-blood\\/blood-facts-and-statistics\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">could require<\\/a>&nbsp;as many as 100 pints of blood.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Blood is essential for human life, and it can\\u2019t be manufactured\\u2014only donated. So these facilities work to build the supply for patients who need it.<\\/p>\"}', 'fasilitas/9Gt8m6IOyRW6ZvVkpA0pCfIOBULfwmSzBalCglwd.jpg', '[]', NULL, '2021-01-09 05:14:07', '2021-01-09 05:14:07', 'blood-banks');
INSERT INTO `fasilitas` VALUES (5, 1, '{\"en\":\"Clinics and medical offices\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">The definition of a&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.merriam-webster.com\\/dictionary\\/clinic\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">clinic<\\/a>&nbsp;is \\u201ca facility for diagnosis and treatment of outpatients.\\u201d There are many healthcare facilities that fit that definition across a wide variety of treatment specialties.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Many people go to a clinic for routine doctor\\u2019s appointments and checkups. These healthcare facilities can be a physician\\u2019s private practice, a group practice setting or a corporately owned clinic that may be connected to a larger healthcare system or hospital.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Clinics cover a lot of ground in healthcare. For example, you could visit a dental clinic to have a toothache investigated, a physical therapy clinic to recover from an athletic injury or a pediatric speech therapy clinic to help your child overcome an articulation disorder.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">If there is a specialized health area you need to see an expert for, then odds are that there\\u2019s a clinic somewhere to accommodate you. The goal of these clinics is to give people preventative care and important diagnoses with as much convenience as possible.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">That goal has also led to \\u201cwalk-in\\u201d clinics becoming situated in grocery and convenience stores, malls and even airports. These clinics allow patients to get a flu shot or receive a prescription without making an appointment at their physician\\u2019s office. While many medical providers believe that a continued relationship with a provider is better for patients\\u2019 long-term health,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\\/pmc\\/articles\\/PMC2834718\\/\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">the speed, convenience and sometimes lower cost<\\/a>&nbsp;of a walk-in clinic can be ideal for a quick need.<\\/p>\"}', 'fasilitas/GFMHqYnSV3bwCDWEM4JdPpJQekWJqJHWO5ZjAyst.jpg', '[]', NULL, '2021-01-09 05:14:30', '2021-01-09 05:14:30', 'clinics-and-medical-offices');
INSERT INTO `fasilitas` VALUES (6, 1, '{\"en\":\"Diabetes education centers\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Diabetes is a very serious illness in the United States. Over 30 million people have diabetes and many of them don\\u2019t know it, reports the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.cdc.gov\\/diabetes\\/basics\\/quick-facts.html\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">Centers for Disease Control<\\/a>&nbsp;(CDC). Additionally, over a third of the national population is highly at risk for diabetes, in a condition called prediabetes.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Patients with diabetes need to manage the disease and typically make lifestyle adjustments to keep it from becoming life-threatening. Since diabetes is so widespread, diabetes education centers rose up to help patients manage their disease and to help people at risk for diabetes to avoid it, if possible.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/diabetes-education.com\\/\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">Diabetes education centers<\\/a>&nbsp;typically offer classes, education, support groups and a variety of resources to help patients manage their diabetes and live as complication-free as possible.<\\/p>\"}', 'fasilitas/q46JKF0itOGXSVzbTD6tXKhKV6V2MyGL74Hbwqmd.jpg', '[]', NULL, '2021-01-09 05:14:57', '2021-01-09 05:14:57', 'diabetes-education-centers');
INSERT INTO `fasilitas` VALUES (7, 1, '{\"en\":\"Dialysis Centers\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-transform: none;\\\">Patients with kidney disease often need regular treatments of dialysis. Dialysis is a process that&nbsp;<\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.healthline.com\\/health\\/dialysis#how-it-works\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; text-transform: none;\\\">filters and cleans<\\/a><span style=\\\"color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-transform: none;\\\">&nbsp;the blood artificially\\u2014the work functioning kidneys normally take on. About&nbsp;<\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.niddk.nih.gov\\/health-information\\/health-statistics\\/kidney-disease\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; text-transform: none;\\\">14 percent<\\/a><span style=\\\"color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-transform: none;\\\">&nbsp;of Americans have chronic kidney disease. When kidneys aren\\u2019t able to filter the blood the way they are supposed to, patients might need dialysis as often as three times a week to avoid serious complications. With such high demand, dialysis facilities rose up to meet patient needs and avoid undue strain on hospitals.<\\/span><br><\\/p>\"}', 'fasilitas/VlrjXgS5q6xNMkFrsEzj6kJVWoi7utjAMJYi88Xu.jpg', '[]', NULL, '2021-01-09 05:15:19', '2021-01-09 05:15:19', 'dailysis-centers');
INSERT INTO `fasilitas` VALUES (8, 1, '{\"en\":\"Hospice homes\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Hospice can be a particularly confusing title. It represents a&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.medicare.gov\\/coverage\\/hospice-and-respite-care.html\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">package of insurance benefits<\\/a>&nbsp;that deals with an end-of-life trajectory. It also represents a philosophy of care provision for dying patients as well as official&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.nhpco.org\\/about\\/hospice-care\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.25); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\\\">networks that offer hospice care<\\/a>. Hospice is also a designation for specific healthcare facilities that specialize in end-of-life care.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Hospice care is a model that provides not only medical support, but also emotional and even spiritual support for patients and their families. According to the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.nhpco.org\\/about\\/hospice-care\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(0, 71, 18); text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 71, 18, 0.75); cursor: pointer; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 150ms ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Klavika, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Cambria, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; outline-width: 0px;\\\">National Hospice and Palliative Care&nbsp;<\\/a>organization, a patient with hospice care has a team of care providers made up of the patient\'s personal physician, a hospice physician, nurses, home health aides, social workers, clergy or other counselors and physical or occupational therapists, if needed.<\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(65, 64, 66); font-family: Flama, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; text-transform: none;\\\">Though patients can receive hospice care at home, if their medical needs are significant, they might live in a nursing home with hospice care, or a specified hospice home.<\\/p>\"}', 'fasilitas/tAVq2L3vlP9ZebI4JMkyC2qGmzCSXun285pSRTyo.jpg', '[]', NULL, '2021-01-09 05:15:45', '2021-01-09 05:15:45', 'hospice-homes');

